body:
### Version of Hardhat

2.14.0

### What happened?

package.json
```json
{
  "name": "hardhat-template",
  "scripts": {
    "flatten": "npx hardhat flatten",
  },
  "license": "MIT",
  "devDependencies": {
    "@ethersproject/abi": "^5.4.7",
    "@ethersproject/providers": "^5.4.7",
